{"body": "I haven't played with mysql2 in long time, but it had issues on Windows (like blocking operations) that made really hard get some stuff done.\n\nThis was caused by the way Ruby 1.8 differs from Ruby 1.9: changes to make Ruby 1.9 work broke Ruby 1.8 functionality.\n\nIf mysql2 works on a version that is only 1.9.x (lets say 0.4 or something) then I think things could work.\n\nI still need to test it out.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5801850", "created_at": "2012-05-19T13:45:03Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6030#issuecomment-5801850", "updated_at": "2012-05-19T13:45:03Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6030, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/luislavena", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/e7cff3cfd41c495e1012227d7dc24202?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F13e5ebb0fa112fe1b31a1067962d74a7.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/received_events", "gravatar_id": "e7cff3cfd41c495e1012227d7dc24202", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "luislavena", "type": "User", "id": 4182, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/luislavena/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52380feebd3543c15100d5d8"}, "id": 5801850, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6030"}
